Use the standard library
This is how to sort_array of arr:
   Remember that n is arr's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that j is 0
      Do this n times:
         When sum of j and 1 is less than n, then:
            When item j in arr is more than item (sum of j and 1) in arr, then:
               Remember that temp is item j in arr
               Remember that item j in arr is item (sum of j and 1) in arr
               Remember that item (sum of j and 1) in arr is temp
            End when
         End when
         Increase j
      End do
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is arr
